Prerequisite:
* Sphinx 1.8.1

To generate documentation run:
```
python setup.py doc
```

Here are some points different from current version:
* The new documentation generated from a templates folder `./doc/python/sphinx` to `./doc/build`.
* The new API reference split into sections to help users jumping between the long list of APIs
* The `grpc_*` modules are included now (though the description is insufficient...)
* If there are warnings or errors in the docstring, it will throw an exception
* A new theme: [Alabaster](https://alabaster.readthedocs.io/en/latest/)
